{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/정규-표현식/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"정규-표현식이란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EA%B7%9C-%ED%91%9C%ED%98%84%EC%8B%9D%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"정규 표현식이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>정규 표현식이란</h2>\n<p>텍스트를 찾고 조작하는 데 쓰는 문자열. </p>\n<h2 id=\"문자-하나-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%ED%95%98%EB%82%98-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"문자 하나 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문자 하나 찾기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"문자-그대로-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EA%B7%B8%EB%8C%80%EB%A1%9C-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"문자 그대로 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문자 그대로 찾기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Hello, my name is Kim. Nice to meet you. my phone number is 000\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">Kim</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">test</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\nstr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">match</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">my</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// [ 'my', 'my' ]</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"모든-문자-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AA%A8%EB%93%A0-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"모든 문자 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>모든 문자 찾기</h3>\n<p>정규 표현식에서는 특별한 문자들(혹은 집합 문자)을 써 무엇을 검색할지 결정한다. <strong>마침표 문자(.)</strong>는 아무 문자 하나와 일치한다. 마침표는 어떠한 문자나 알파벳, 숫자, 심지어 문자 부호로 쓰인 마침표(.) 자체와도 일치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  text1.txt\n  image.png\n  file.txt\n  test.txt\n  image2.jpeg\n  image.jpg\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">.txt</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>마침표를 연속으로 사용하면 어떠한 문자든 붙어있는 마침표 개수만큼 일치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n  text1.txt\n  image.png\n  file.txt\n  test.txt\n  image2.jpeg\n  image.jpg\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">....txt</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"특수문자-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%88%98%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"특수문자 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특수문자 찾기</h3>\n<p>마침표는 정규 표현식에서 특별한 의미가 있다. 마침표를 찾으려고 한다면 마침표 앞에 역슬래시(\\)를 붙이면 된다. <code class=\"language-text\">\\.</code>은 마침표 자체와 일치한다. 정규 표현식에서는 특수 문자 자체와 일치하는 패턴을 찾을 때 역슬래시를 사용하면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">text1.txt</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">\\.txt</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"문자-집합으로-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%A7%91%ED%95%A9%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"문자 집합으로 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문자 집합으로 찾기</h2>\n<p>문자 집합을 사용하면 특정 문자들과 문자 범위를 일치시킬 수 있다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"여러-문자-중-하나와-일치시키기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%97%AC%EB%9F%AC-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%A4%91-%ED%95%98%EB%82%98%EC%99%80-%EC%9D%BC%EC%B9%98%EC%8B%9C%ED%82%A4%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"여러 문자 중 하나와 일치시키기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>여러 문자 중 하나와 일치시키기</h3>\n<p>정규표현식에서는 메타 문자인 대괄호([])를 이용해 문자 집합을 표현한다. 대괄호 안에 있는 문자는 모두 집합의 구성원이 되며, 집합에 속한 문자 가운데 하나가 일치한다. AND가 아닌 OR로 동작.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\nna1.xls\nna2.xls\nsa1.xls\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">[ns]a[0-9].xls</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>A-Z는 A부터 Z사이에 있는 모든 대문자와 일치</li>\n<li>a-z는 a부터 z사이에 있는 모든 소문자와 일치</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n&lt;div color=\"#fff000\" text=\"#333737\" />\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">#[0-9A-Fa-f][0-9A-Fa-f][0-9A-Fa-f][0-9A-Fa-f][0-9A-Fa-f][0-9A-Fa-f]</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"제외하고-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%9C%EC%99%B8%ED%95%98%EA%B3%A0-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"제외하고 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>제외하고 찾기</h3>\n<p>캐럿 (^) 문자를 사용해서 제외할 문자 집합을 지정한다. 캐럿 문자는 이 문자 바로 뒤에 있는 문자나 범위뿐만 아니라 집합 안에 있는 문자나 범위를 모두 제외한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\nnam.xls\nna1.xls\nna2.xls\nsa1.xls\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">[ns]a[^0-9].xls</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"메타-문자-사용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A9%94%ED%83%80-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"메타 문자 사용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>메타 문자 사용하기</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\nif (myArray[0] === 0)\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">myArray\\[[0-9]\\]</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">exec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"공백-문자-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B3%B5%EB%B0%B1-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"공백 문자 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>공백 문자 찾기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">[\\b] 역스페이스\n\\f 페이지 넘김(form feed)\n\\n 줄바꿈\n\\r 캐리지 리턴\n\\t 탭\n\\v 수직탭</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"숫자와-숫자가-아닌-문자-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%88%AB%EC%9E%90%EC%99%80-%EC%88%AB%EC%9E%90%EA%B0%80-%EC%95%84%EB%8B%8C-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"숫자와 숫자가 아닌 문자 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>숫자와 숫자가 아닌 문자 찾기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">\\d 숫자 하나([0-9]와 같다)\n\\D 숫자를 제외한 문자 하나([^0-9]와 같다)</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\nif (myArray[0] === 0)\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">myArray\\[[\\d]\\]</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">exec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"영숫자-문자와-영숫자가-아닌-문자-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%81%EC%88%AB%EC%9E%90-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90%EC%99%80-%EC%98%81%EC%88%AB%EC%9E%90%EA%B0%80-%EC%95%84%EB%8B%8C-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"영숫자 문자와 영숫자가 아닌 문자 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>영숫자 문자와 영숫자가 아닌 문자 찾기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">\\w 대소문자와 밑줄을 포함하는 모든 영숫자([a-zA-Z0-9_]와 같다)\n\\W 영숫자나, 밑줄이 아닌 모든 문자([^a-zA-Z0-9_]와 같다)</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"공백-문자와-공백이-아닌-문자-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B3%B5%EB%B0%B1-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90%EC%99%80-%EA%B3%B5%EB%B0%B1%EC%9D%B4-%EC%95%84%EB%8B%8C-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"공백 문자와 공백이 아닌 문자 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>공백 문자와 공백이 아닌 문자 찾기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">\\s 모든 공백 문자([\\f\\n\\r\\t\\v]와 같다)\n\\S 공백 문자가 아닌 모든 문자([^\\f\\n\\r\\t\\v]와 같다)</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"반복-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%98%EB%B3%B5-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"반복 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>반복 찾기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"문자-하나-이상-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%ED%95%98%EB%82%98-%EC%9D%B4%EC%83%81-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"문자 하나 이상 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문자 하나 이상 찾기</h3>\n<p>문자나 집합에 속한 요소를 하나 이상 찾으려면 문자 뒤에 더하기(+) 문자를 붙이면 된다. 더하기(+)는 문자가 하나 이상일 때 일치한다. a가 a를 찾는 데 반해, a+는 하나 이상 연속된 a를 찾는다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n1. khw@yahoo.com\n2. yellow@naver.com\n3. hello@google.com\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">\\w+@\\w+\\.\\w+</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>더하기(+)는 문자 집합이 하나 이상인 경우에도 사용한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n1. khw@yahoo.com\n2. yellow@naver.co.kr\n3. hello@google.co.kr\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">[\\w]+@[\\w.]+\\.\\w+</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"문자가-없는-경우나-하나-이상-연속하는-문자-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90%EA%B0%80-%EC%97%86%EB%8A%94-%EA%B2%BD%EC%9A%B0%EB%82%98-%ED%95%98%EB%82%98-%EC%9D%B4%EC%83%81-%EC%97%B0%EC%86%8D%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"문자가 없는 경우나 하나 이상 연속하는 문자 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문자가 없는 경우나 하나 이상 연속하는 문자 찾기</h3>\n<p>더하기(+)는 하나 이상 연속된 문자를 찾는다. 문자가 없는 경우는 아예 찾지 못하고, 최소한 하나는 일치해야 한다. 있을 수도 있고 없을 수도 있는 문자와 일치시키려면 메타 문자인 별표(*)를 사용해야 한다. 별표(*)는 문자나 집합 바로 뒤에 두면 찾고자 하는 문자나 집합이 없는 경우 또는 하나 이상 연속하는 경우에 일치한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n1. khw@yahoo.com\n2. yellow@naver.co.kr\n3. hello.world@google.co.kr\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">\\w+[\\w.]*@[\\w.]+\\.\\w+</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"문자가-없거나-하나인-문자-찾기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90%EA%B0%80-%EC%97%86%EA%B1%B0%EB%82%98-%ED%95%98%EB%82%98%EC%9D%B8-%EB%AC%B8%EC%9E%90-%EC%B0%BE%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"문자가 없거나 하나인 문자 찾기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문자가 없거나 하나인 문자 찾기</h3>\n<p>물음표(?)는 문자가 있는 경우 일치하고 문자가 없어도 일치하지만, 별표(*)와 달리 문자나 집합이 없거나 하나만 있는 경우만 일치하며, 하나 이상은 일치하지 않는다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n1. http://www.google.com/\n2. https://www.google.com/\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">https?:\\/\\/[\\w./]+</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"구간-지정하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B5%AC%EA%B0%84-%EC%A7%80%EC%A0%95%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"구간 지정하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>구간 지정하기</h3>\n<p>연속하는 문자를 찾을 떄 검색 조건을 더 구체적으로 지정하고자 정규 표현식에서는 구간을 사용한다. 구간은 중괄호({})안에 표시한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n1. #336433\n2. #ffff33\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">#\\w{6}</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>범위 구간을 찾기 위해선 {2, 4}와 같은 형식으로 표현한다. 최소 구간을 찾기 위해서는 {3,}과 같이 표현하면 된다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n1. 010-1111-2222\n2. 02-342-2344\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">\\d{2,3}[-]\\d{3,4}[-]\\d{4}</span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"과하게-일치하는-상황-방지하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B3%BC%ED%95%98%EA%B2%8C-%EC%9D%BC%EC%B9%98%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%83%81%ED%99%A9-%EB%B0%A9%EC%A7%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"과하게 일치하는 상황 방지하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>과하게 일치하는 상황 방지하기</h3>\n<p>별표와 더하기 같은 메타 문자는 탐욕적 수량자이다. 가능한 큰 덩어리를 찾으려 한다는 뜻이다. 탐욕적 수량자에는 모두 각각 대응되는 게으른 수량자가 있다. 탐욕적 수량자는 텍스트 마지막에서 시작해 거꾸로 찾는다. 의도적으로 수량자를 탐욕적으로 설계했기 때문이다. 게으른 수량자는 기존 수량자 뒤에 물음표를 붙여 표현한다.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>탐욕적 수량자</th>\n<th>게으른 수량자</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>*</td>\n<td>*?</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>+</td>\n<td>+?</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>{n,}</td>\n<td>{n,}?</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> str <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">\n&lt;h1>hello&lt;/h1> and &lt;h2>world&lt;/h2>\n</span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">&lt;h[\\d]>.*&lt;\\/h[\\d]></span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>str<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">matchAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token regex\"><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-source language-regex\">&lt;h[\\d]>.*?&lt;\\/h[\\d]></span><span class=\"token regex-delimiter\">/</span><span class=\"token regex-flags\">g</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"reference__md\">\n[참고]<br/>손에 잡히는 정규표현식, 벤 포터 저. 인사이트\n</div>","timeToRead":7,"excerpt":"…","fields":{"slug":"/posts/정규-표현식/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"정규 표현식","status":"published","description":"정규 표현식에 관한 공부","date":"December 10, 2019","categories":["programming"],"tags":["programming","regular expression"],"template":"posts","thumbnail":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/정규-표현식/","previous":{"id":"0b640361-2981-5fac-ae16-627018d2b94c","frontmatter":{"title":"함수형 자바스크립트","tags":["javascript","programming","functional programming"],"categories":["javascript"],"template":"posts","status":"published"},"fields":{"slug":"/posts/함수형-자바스크립트/"}},"next":{"id":"2589903a-4c3d-5c43-af88-487d62b8d7b2","frontmatter":{"title":"정렬 Sorting","tags":["programming","algorithm","sorting"],"categories":["programming"],"template":"posts","status":"published"},"fields":{"slug":"/posts/정렬-sorting/"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}